EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 1600Z DAILY
   09 THRU 11 MAY WITHIN 15 MILES OF 57-16N 008-05W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 111700Z MAY.
